# ============================================================
# WhimAdmin — local additions to project-root .gitignore
# ============================================================
#
# The root .gitignore handles `var/` and `.tmp_*` recursively
# (those patterns have no slash, so they match at any depth).
#
# This file only needs to add what the root pattern misses:
# `_docs/audits/` in the root has a slash in the middle, so it
# matches only the root-level path. The whimadmin/_docs/audits/
# tree needs its own rule here.

# Internal hardening notes / per-session audit reports.
# Not part of the public WhimAdmin distribution.
_docs/audits/
